#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    vec3 p,r=iResolution,c=vec3(0),
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1));
 	for(float i=0.,s,e,g=0.,t=iTime;i++<90.;){
        p=g*d;
        p=R(p,normalize(H(t*.02)*2.-1.),g/8.);
        p+=vec3(1.*cos(t*.05),.5*sin(t*.1),t*.8);
        p=asin(sin(p*.8));
        s=1.6;
        for(int j=0;j++<7;)
           p=.5-abs(p.zxy);
           s*=e=max(1.2/dot(p,p),1.),
           p=R(p*e-vec3(.5,.1,.5),vec3(.577),-1.5);
        g+=e=abs(p.x)/s+5e-5;
	    c+=mix(vec3(1),H(log(s)*.06),.8)*.04/exp(.4*i*i*e);
	}
	c*=c*c*c;
    O=vec4(c,1);
}
